# Monitoring & Analytics Rules

## System Monitoring
- **Performance Metrics**: Track response times, throughput, and resource usage
- **Health Checks**: Implement comprehensive health check endpoints
- **Alerting**: Set up intelligent alerting for critical issues
- **Dashboards**: Create meaningful monitoring dashboards

## User Analytics
- **Behavior Tracking**: Monitor user interactions and patterns
- **Feature Usage**: Track which features are used most frequently
- **Performance Impact**: Measure how changes affect user experience
- **Error Tracking**: Monitor and analyze user-facing errors

## Application Metrics
- **Business Metrics**: Track key performance indicators
- **Technical Metrics**: Monitor system performance and reliability
- **User Experience**: Measure user satisfaction and engagement
- **Conversion Tracking**: Monitor user journey completion rates

## Logging Standards
- **Structured Logging**: Use consistent, structured log formats
- **Log Levels**: Implement appropriate log levels (DEBUG, INFO, WARN, ERROR)
- **Context Preservation**: Include relevant context in log messages
- **Log Aggregation**: Centralize logs for analysis and monitoring

## Data Collection
- **Privacy Compliance**: Respect user privacy and data protection regulations
- **Data Minimization**: Collect only necessary data
- **Consent Management**: Obtain proper consent for data collection
- **Data Retention**: Implement appropriate data retention policies

## Analysis & Insights
- **Real-time Analytics**: Provide real-time insights into system performance
- **Trend Analysis**: Identify patterns and trends in data
- **Predictive Analytics**: Use data to predict future behavior and needs
- **Actionable Insights**: Provide insights that lead to concrete actions

## Reporting
- **Automated Reports**: Generate regular reports on key metrics
- **Custom Dashboards**: Create customizable dashboards for different stakeholders
- **Alert Reports**: Provide detailed reports when issues occur
- **Performance Reports**: Regular performance and optimization reports